NAME Mouse Jiggler
DESCRIPTION Keeps screen awake by jiggling the mouse at random intervals
CATEGORY post
PLATFORMS WIN,MAC,LINUX
OPTION DURATION 60 "Jiggle duration in seconds (approx)"
OPTION INTERVAL 5000 "Interval between jiggles (ms)"
PLATFORM ALL
REM Platform-independent mouse jiggler using PLATFORM ALL
VAR $count = 0
REPEAT_BLOCK {{DURATION}}
MOUSE_MOVE 3 0
DELAY 50
MOUSE_MOVE -3 0
DELAY 50
MOUSE_MOVE 0 3
DELAY 50
MOUSE_MOVE 0 -3
DELAY {{INTERVAL}}
END_REPEAT
LED_COLOR GREEN
